metadata.name: STANIFLOU X METAKICKS 1906D #1
metadata.description: The Metakicks 1906D is a special collaboration crafted with french sneaker artist Stan Birch (Staniflou), a tribute to creativity and the future of Streetwear culture. Only 25 hand-customized physical sneakers linked to 25 Metakicks. Please note: the Metakicks version is a digital asset acting as a pass unlocking special access to retail drops, free drops & private drops on Physical Streetwear items from various brands and from Stan. You can unlock those accesses on https://metakicks.sneakmart.com/inventory and soon to come directly on the Sneakmart app.
